OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,FA Russian man has been jailed for four
OL,7,Fyears for assaulting a woman in an
OL,8,Fattack which was witnessed on a video
OL,9,Fcall by Donald Trump's youngest son
OL,10,FBarron.
OL,12,FMatvei Rumiantsev, 23, drunkenly beat
OL,13,Fup the victim when he became jealous
OL,14,Fof her blossoming friendship with Mr
OL,15,FTrump, 19, after she met him through
OL,16,Fsocial media.
OL,18,FDuring the assault, he answered a
OL,19,FFaceTime call on her phone from Mr
OL,20,FTrump and turned the camera to show
OL,21,Fher crying on the floor.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,FIn a 999 call to City of London Police
OL,7,Fon January 18 last year, the US
OL,8,Fpresident's son pleaded for help for
OL,9,Fthe woman, telling the operator: "It's
OL,10,Freally an emergency.
OL,12,F"I'm calling from the US, uh I just
OL,13,Fgot a call from a girl, you know,
OL,14,Fshe's getting beat up."
OL,16,FThe woman herself managed to call 999
OL,17,Fafter enduring violence lasting an
OL,18,Fhour, telling the operator: "Please
OL,19,Fhelp me, I'm gonna get killed."
OL,26,@qD@bOUtD@AOUvD@WO]zD@]OU{D@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
