OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,FAt Snaresbrook Crown Court on Friday,
OL,7,FRumiantsev ` described as a "trained
OL,8,Ffighter" ` was sentenced by Mr Justice
OL,9,FBennathan to four years in prison for
OL,10,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm
OL,11,Fand perverting the course of justice.
OL,13,F"You are a man given to jealousy and
OL,14,Fyou have a temper", said the judge,
OL,15,Fbefore criticising Rumiantsev for
OL,16,Fbeing "totally unrepentant" and
OL,17,Ffailing to accept blame for the attack.
OL,26,@oD@]OUpD@HO]uD@AOUvD@RO]xD@GOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,F"Your lack of insight and empathy was
OL,7,Fapparent at trial. You continue to try
OL,8,Fto blame the complainant for
OL,9,Feverything that has happened."
OL,11,FHe pointed to a letter from Rumiantsev
OL,12,Fsaid his actions that night had been
OL,13,F"inappropriate", telling him: "That's
OL,14,Fa very long way from you facing up to
OL,15,Fthe simple truth of what happened that
OL,16,Fnight."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]uD@AOUuD@OO]uD@_OUxD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
