FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,FHe said the evidence shows Rumiantsev
OL,7,Fhad repeatedly struck the woman over
OL,8,Fthe course of an hour, dragged her by
OL,9,Fher hair when she tried to seek help,
OL,10,Fand leaving her believing she "might
OL,11,Fdie".
OL,13,FAfter his arrest, Rumiantsev made
OL,14,F"repeated efforts" to try to avoid
OL,15,Fjustice by convincing the woman to
OL,16,Fwithdraw her allegations, with a phone
OL,17,Fcall from the police station and a
OL,18,Fletter to a friend while he was in
OL,19,Fprison.
OL,26,@rD@_OUsD@DO]vD@AOUvD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
