FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,F"I didn't expect her to pick up due to
OL,7,Fthe difference in the time zone to the
OL,8,Ffact I am in the USA, the phone was
OL,9,Fanswered but not by her, to my
OL,10,Fdismay," he wrote.
OL,12,F"The individual who picked up the
OL,13,Fphone was a shirtless man with darkish
OL,14,Fhair, although I didn't get a good
OL,15,Flook, this view lasted maybe one
OL,16,Fsecond and I was racing with
OL,17,Fadrenaline.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
