OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,F"The camera was then flipped to the
OL,7,Fvictim getting hit while crying,
OL,8,Fstating something in Russian. The guy
OL,9,Fhad hung up. This whole interaction
OL,10,Fhad lasted five to seven seconds."
OL,12,FThe victim of the attack said she
OL,13,Fbelieves Rumiantsev deliberately
OL,14,Fanswered the FaceTime call and showed
OL,15,Fher crying and screaming on the floor
OL,16,Fas a form of punishment.
OL,18,FProsecutor Serena Gates KC said: "She
OL,19,Fthinks the phone call was answered and
OL,20,Fthe assault shown on video because the
OL,21,Fdefendant wanted an audience."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]zD@bOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
