OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,FThe judge praised Mr Trump's actions,
OL,7,Fsaying he had "properly and
OL,8,Fresponsibly" alerted the emergency
OL,9,Fservices despite being in the US.
OL,11,FAt trial, Ms Gates said Rumiantsev was
OL,12,Fjealous of the woman's friendship with
OL,13,FBarron Trump, perhaps because of his
OL,14,F"public profile".She told jurors to
OL,15,Fnote Mr Trump's "urgent" and "worried"
OL,16,Ftone in the call to police.
OL,18,FThe court had heard Rumiantsev and the
OL,19,Fwoman had been drinking together on
OL,20,Fthe evening of January 17, 2025 and
OL,21,Finto the early hours of the next day.
OL,26,@oD@OOUpD@LO]vD@AOUvD@PO]wD@QOUwD@XO]wD@
OL,26,A^OUwD@fO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
