PN,40811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,FThe prosecution said Rumiantsev, who
OL,7,Fcomes from a wealthy family and has
OL,8,Fmartial arts training, assaulted the
OL,9,Fwoman that day, including hitting her
OL,10,Fin the face.
OL,12,FWhen he answered her phone during the
OL,13,Fbeating to a FaceTime call from Mr
OL,14,FTrump, he turned the screen to the
OL,15,Fwoman who was crying and screaming on
OL,16,Fthe floor.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,FIn his phone call to police, Mr Trump
OL,7,Fwas initially coy about how he knew
OL,8,Fthe woman and when asked he replied:
OL,9,F"I mean these details don't matter,
OL,10,Fshe's getting beat up."
OL,12,FAfter being admonished by the operator
OL,13,Ffor being "rude" and not answering
OL,14,Fquestions, Mr Trump said: "I met her
OL,15,Fon social media."
OL,17,FThe court heard Rumiantsev became
OL,18,Faware of the woman's friendship with
OL,19,FMr Trump in October 2024, and during
OL,20,Fquestioning at trial he described
OL,21,Fhimself as "jealous to some extent".
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@WO]uD@KOUuD@PO]vD@[OUwD@QO]}D@
OL,26,ALOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
