PN,40813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1774865180
OL,3,CMan jailed for attacking woman in
OL,4,Cassault witnessed by Barron Trump
OL,6,FHe added: "What I was really unhappy
OL,7,Fabout was that she was frankly leading
OL,8,Fhim (Barron Trump) on."In a report
OL,9,Ffrom counselling sessions which was
OL,10,Fhanded to the judge, Rumiantsev was
OL,11,Fsaid to be "taking responsibility for
OL,12,Fhis own shortcomings".
OL,14,FThe judge said Rumiantsev may be
OL,15,Fdeported from the UK as a consequence
OL,16,Fof his convictions.
OL,26,@nD@KOUpD@WO]sD@LOUtD@UO]
